{"tid":772982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網戀「美國女軍官」 港老翁被騙200萬","createTime":"2018-08-09T07:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T04:52:22.000Z","uid":184679,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"45db5c3fb436ac7445b6dba89d5f3bdbdb43a1a5","tid":772982,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:25:12.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】近年相繼有本港女子在網上戀上「美國軍人」而被騙巨款，最近亦有宗同類案件，中招的是73歲香港老翁，他被自稱美軍軍官的女子詐騙，由去年底至今年5月，先後匯款共約200萬元給對方，至上月始醒覺被騙報警。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>長者中心上fb結識</strong><br />\n<br />\n警方指出，73歲陳姓男事主於上月2日報案，稱自己於2017年11月透過網上社交平台認識一名女子，對方以不同理由向他索取金錢。據了解，陳翁去年11月在長者中心上網時，在facebook認識一名自稱為美國女軍官的網友，兩人在網絡世界中情投意合，令陳翁誤信自己開展了一段新戀情。<br />\n<strong><br />\n女方稱禮物遭扣關要錢贖</strong><br />\n<br />\n該女軍官其後屢以不同理由索取金錢，例如報稱自己有多件送給陳翁的包裹被海關扣起，需要陳先行代付相關費用才能領回，結果陳翁自去年12月至今年5月間，將200萬元先後分開存入一個外地戶口及3個本地戶口。陳其後與該名「女軍官」失去聯絡，始懷疑自己受騙，於是到中區警署報警。警方經初步調查後，將案列作「以欺騙手段取得財產」，交由中區警區刑事調查隊第8隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方上月底公布今年上半年罪案數字，當中網上情緣騙案由去年同期78宗，激增至今年272宗，而受害人損失的總金額，亦由去年上半年的364萬元，急升至今年同期的1.374億元。警務處刑事及保安處處長李志恒早前指出，網上情緣的騙徒一般訛稱海外專業人士或軍人，透過社交媒體結交受害人，再以各種藉口要求受害人付錢，例如生意失敗要求匯錢應急等，而受害人以女性為主。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180809/s00002/1533752236284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180809%2Fs00002%2F1533752236284&d=aQF%2BqNc8xvVqZsVdJcXYY0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=916d346e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180809%2Fs00002%2F1533752236284&h=90594e75\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180809/s00002/1533752236284</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ijGKciq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FijGKciq.jpg&h=9e7b556d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d044d1b542b46032a599fa0fe77d1de4e096e852","tid":772982,"uid":63909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"73歲陳姓男事主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b998fb43a82511a6fc85d16b6300f2c163432a2e","tid":772982,"uid":39855,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"好想知女軍官講咩文？"},{"pid":"871affc65049bfb72a9df2fc9e6d7f587c09795f","tid":772982,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:34:35.000Z","msg":"一百歳唔死都有新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67806af8f69a4d3c37190e617a93ac4740b26a3a","tid":772982,"uid":146621,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:38:52.000Z","msg":"廢老食鹽多過你食米<br />\n點解咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc58a74b7a33997687f89a9f6669429d573ca93","tid":772982,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"係咪美女軍官呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9782988c4157af94cbd5adcb3d4432d25f7861","tid":772982,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:41:11.000Z","msg":"真愛"},{"pid":"501f11ae7a09f836374775aa226a54965cfcea6a","tid":772982,"uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img2.cache.netease.com/cnews/2010/2/24/201002241157474d358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.cache.netease.com%2Fcnews%2F2010%2F2%2F24%2F201002241157474d358.jpg&h=4058b296&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c64f2cd95fd4739611133e634070e259371d042","tid":772982,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T08:06:02.000Z","msg":"睇錯聯邦女軍官<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma